{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856829625,"sessionID":"ses_286b4886fffej46k80vZS1AYFy","part":{"id":"prt_d79504980001ALakwzEpY6tLBk","messageID":"msg_d7950189b001X0I1xsPqIfL8tS","sessionID":"ses_286b4886fffej46k80vZS1AYFy","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:22","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: id: AR-008\n2: title: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n3: module: pkg/workloadmanager\n4: language: Go\n5: size: S\n6: status: open\n7: \n8: # AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n9: # Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n10: # Language: Go\n11: # Size: S\n12: \n13: # OpenSpec Metadata\n14: openspec:\n15:   version: \"1.0\"\n16:   project: agentcube\n17: \n18: # Architecture Requirement\n19: requirement:\n20:   type: garbage-collection\n21:   description: |\n22:     Implement a scheduled garbage collection mechanism for sandbox resources.\n23:     This component periodically scans and cleans up expired, idle, or orphaned\n24:     sandbox instances to reclaim resources and maintain system health. It provides\n25:     configurable retention policies, cleanup strategies, and observability hooks.\n26: \n27: # Scope\n28: scope:\n29:   in:\n30:     - Scheduled GC task with configurable interval\n31:     - Expired sandbox detection based on TTL\n32:     - Idle sandbox detection based on inactivity timeout\n33:     - Orphaned sandbox cleanup (owner not found)\n34:     - Resource reclamation metrics\n35:     - Graceful cleanup with proper finalization\n36:     - Configurable retention policies per sandbox type\n37:     - Safe-mode dry-run capability\n38:     - Event logging for audit trail\n39:   out:\n40:     - Sandbox lifecycle management (handled in AR-005/AR-006)\n41:     - CRD reconciler logic (handled in AR-007)\n42:     - Multi-cluster GC coordination (separate AR)\n43:     - External storage cleanup (separate AR)\n44: \n45: # Acceptance Criteria\n46: acceptance:\n47:   - GC runs at configurable intervals (default: 5 minutes)\n48:   - Expired sandboxes are identified and cleaned up\n49:   - Idle sandboxes are detected and reclaimed\n50:   - Orphaned resources are properly handled\n51:   - Metrics exposed for GC operations and reclaimed resources\n52:   - Safe-mode allows dry-run without actual deletion\n53:   - Audit logging for all cleanup operations\n54:   - Unit tests achieve >= 80% coverage\n55:   - Integration tests verify end-to-end GC flow\n56: \n57: # References\n58: references:\n59:   - AR-005: Sandbox Creation Handler\n60:   - AR-006: Sandbox Deletion and Lifecycle Management\n61:   - AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n62: \n63: # Estimation\n64: estimation:\n65:   size: S\n66:   story_points: 3\n67:   days: 2\n\n(End of file - total 67 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: AR-008\ntitle: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\nmodule: pkg/workloadmanager\nlanguage: Go\nsize: S\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n# Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n# Language: Go\n# Size: S\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: garbage-collection","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775856829602,"end":1775856829622}}}}
